<span class="ez_quot">&gt; </span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; Ideas / Needs:</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; -- Delayed Reports: Two (or more) classes of user, public and private.</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; Private users see real-time reports. Public users see reports delayed by X</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; days.</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; -- Suite of SMS tools - including SMS Automate and SMS Parse (comparing</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; incoming SMS in the local language and slang to a database of keywords to</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; pinpoint location and other information)</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; -- Suite of Mapping Tools - enhancing/updating layers to overlay on Google</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; Maps - the area is poorly mapped, and needs a lot of work.</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; </span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; At this moment, we are not sure what our budget is - so I would be</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; interested to talk to those with Ushahidi experience to get an idea of</span>
what
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; this might cost.</span>
<span class="ez_quot">&gt; </span>
